(and over 43,000 students system-wide), 350 degree programs, and a 
nationally-ranked library system. Columbia, the capital of South 
Carolina, has a population of over 650,000 in the greater metropolitan 
area. The University of South Carolina is an affirmative action/equal 
opportunity employer. Minorities and women are encouraged to apply. The 
University of South Carolina does not discriminate in educational or 
